   By contrast, UTIR/receipts are described as the durable evidence stream used to audit and reproduce actions:

```570:579:/Users/jobs/Desktop/tmp-meta3-engine-test/_export/meta3-canonical/docs/tribench-v2/artifacts/tribench_v2.hypergraph.json
